{
  "id": "adv_event_2204_01_03",
  "title": "ラブストーリーは突然に",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、まずは一通り聴かせてくれないか\n『Precious』は歌えるよな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ could you let me listen to it first?\nCan you sing \"Precious\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.2949658393000005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、歌えますわ\n尊敬する麻奈様の大好きな曲ですから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I can sing it.\nIt's a beloved song of Mana-sama‚ whom I admire…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5,
      "endTime": 13.1382992745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "歌えはするんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can sing it‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.3333333333,
      "endTime": 15.9986847718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　どうした？　なんだか元気がないぞ\n顔色悪くないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? What's wrong? You seem a bit down.\nAre you feeling unwell?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.7,
      "endTime": 22.7763567607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんでもありません！\n私は出来る子、私は出来る子……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No‚ it's nothing!\nI'm capable‚ I'm capable…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9666666667,
      "endTime": 29.6268932979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "ファイッ、すず！　さあ、元気をお出しなさい！\n元気があればなんでも出来る！　らしいですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ Suzu! Come on‚ show your energy!\nIf I have energy‚ I can do anything! Apparently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8333333333,
      "endTime": 38.4990931829,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……何をぶつぶつ言ってるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What are you muttering about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.7,
      "endTime": 41.333333333300004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "これは自己暗示をかけて――\nいえ、なんでもありませんわ。早く曲を流して下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is self-affirmation…\nNo‚ it's nothing. Please play the song quickly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.4333333333,
      "endTime": 48.9570711688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、じゃあいくぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ then let's begin.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.1666666667,
      "endTime": 51.537324158400004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "――ごくり、すずファイッですわ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gulp It's Suzu-fight!…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7333333333,
      "endTime": 55.266666666700004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― Two hours later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.0666666667,
      "endTime": 57.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……全然ダメです……\n{user}さん、もう一度、お願いしますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa‚ haa… It's completely no good…\n{user}-san‚ please once again‚ I beg you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.7666666667,
      "endTime": 69.2841665744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……いや、今日はもうやめておこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ let's stop for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4666666667,
      "endTime": 72.1666667621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "そんな、まだです！　まだ私は歌えますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's not over yet! I can still sing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3666666667,
      "endTime": 76.8447391192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてやめるのか分からないのか？\n今日のすず、声が全然出ていないんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't you understand why we're stopping?\nYour voice isn't coming out at all today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0333333333,
      "endTime": 83.843743406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.0333333333,
      "endTime": 85.319773217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いつもなら、自分で気付いているはずだ\nどうしたんだ？　どこか具合が悪いのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Normally‚ you would notice it yourself.\nWhat's wrong? Are you feeling unwell somewhere?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.5333333333,
      "endTime": 92.33666176409999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "……実は、昨日、麻奈様のライブ映像を\nずっと観て研究をしたのですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Actually‚ yesterday‚ I watched Mana-sama's video…\nAnd I studied it for a long time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5333333333,
      "endTime": 99.639319805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、昨日寝てないのか？\nそれじゃあ調子が悪いのは当たり前だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be that you didn't sleep yesterday?\nThat's why you're not feeling well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8333333333,
      "endTime": 105.96015591129999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "あの、{user}さん、私、分かりませんの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ {user}-san‚ I don't understand…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.1666666667,
      "endTime": 111.97920653029999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "どうして、麻奈様の曲を私が歌うのか……\n{user}さんが、私を選んだのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why am I the one singing Mana-sama's songs…\nWhy did you choose me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1666666667,
      "endTime": 120.40929716420001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……。俺の説明不足で\nすずを悩ませてしまったんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… It's because of my lack of explanation.\nI've caused Suzu to worry. I'm sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.6333333333,
      "endTime": 126.7537330274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "すまない。ちゃんと説明するから、外に出よう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll explain properly‚ let's go outside.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.9666666667,
      "endTime": 130.8272788684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "はい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.2333333333,
      "endTime": 132.1508163531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "（ああ、私の体調管理ミスで{user}さんに）\n（心配を掛けてしまって……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Ah‚ because of my poor health management‚ )\n(I've caused {user}-san to…worry about me…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2,
      "endTime": 140.1448047724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "（プロのアイドルになったのに、情けないですわ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Even though I've become a professional idol‚ how pathetic…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5333333333,
      "endTime": 144.5175963243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "――先方の企画意図を聞いて\n未来に対して前向きな曲がいいと俺は思ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― After listening to the intentions of the counterparty.\nI thought a positive song about future would be good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.8333333333,
      "endTime": 152.60349857699998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "それで、麻奈の楽曲の中から『Precious』を\n選んだんだ。選曲はいいと思うんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I chose \"Precious\" from Mana's songs.\nI think the song selection is good‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.8,
      "endTime": 159.6390475999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_03-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "はあ、そうですわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ yes‚ I suppose so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.8333333333,
      "endTime": 162.76639450390002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
